1. 	To create a hidden file/folder: mkdir .hiddenfileorfoldername


	To display hidden files/folders: ls -a


2. 	To create nested directories at once: 

	mkdir -p /these/folders/are/just/for/fun


3. 	Executing commands:

	echo "test" > fun
	echo "another test" >> fun
	wc -c fun

	Output: 18 fun


4. 	To append something in the file without a newline character:

	echo -n “test" > fun
	echo -n “another test" >> fun
	cat fun

	Output: testanother test
